# Import Rules

## Import Order (Strict)

Imports **MUST** be grouped in this exact order:

1. **External packages** (React, Next.js, third-party)
2. **Internal absolute imports** (`@/...`)
3. **Relative imports** (`../`, `./`)
4. **Style imports** (`.css`, `.scss`, etc.)

### Pattern
```typescript
// 1. External packages
import React from "react";
import { useDispatch } from "react-redux";
import type { Metadata } from "next";

// 2. Internal absolute imports
import { useAppDispatch } from "@/hooks/useAppDispatch";
import { BasePanel } from "@/components/base-panel";
import { setImage } from "@/state/imageSlice";

// 3. Relative imports
import { UploadButton } from "./upload-button";
import { UploadInstructions } from "./upload-instructions";

// 4. Style imports
import "./styles.css";
```

## Import Style

### Prefer Absolute Imports
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - absolute import
import { useAppDispatch } from "@/hooks/useAppDispatch";
import { BasePanel } from "@/components/base-panel";

// ❌ WRONG - relative when absolute available
import { useAppDispatch } from "../../hooks/useAppDispatch";
import { BasePanel } from "../base-panel/base-panel";
```

### Use Named Imports
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - named import
import { ComponentName } from "@/components/component-name";

// ❌ WRONG - default import for named export
import ComponentName from "@/components/component-name";
```

### Type Imports
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - separate type imports
import type { ComponentProps } from "@/types";
import { Component } from "@/components/component";

// ✅ ALSO CORRECT - inline type import
import { Component, type ComponentProps } from "@/components/component";
```

## Import Grouping Rules

### Separate Groups with Blank Lines
```typescript
// External
import React from "react";

// Internal absolute
import { useAppDispatch } from "@/hooks/useAppDispatch";

// Relative
import { LocalComponent } from "./local-component";

// Styles
import "./styles.css";
```

### Sort Within Groups
- Alphabetically within each group (optional but recommended)
- Type imports before value imports

## Common Violations

### Violation: Wrong Order
```typescript
// ❌ WRONG
import { BasePanel } from "@/components/base-panel";
import React from "react";
import "./styles.css";
import { LocalComponent } from "./local";

// ✅ CORRECT
import React from "react";
import { BasePanel } from "@/components/base-panel";
import { LocalComponent } from "./local";
import "./styles.css";
```

### Violation: Relative Instead of Absolute
```typescript
// ❌ WRONG
import { useAppDispatch } from "../../hooks/useAppDispatch";

// ✅ CORRECT
import { useAppDispatch } from "@/hooks/useAppDispatch";
```

### Violation: Default Import for Named Export
```typescript
// ❌ WRONG
import BasePanel from "@/components/base-panel";

// ✅ CORRECT
import { BasePanel } from "@/components/base-panel";
```
